Maintainer: Robin K. S. Hankin <hankin.robin@gmail.com>
Description: This
 package furnishes functionality to work with Lorentz transforms in special
 relativity.  It also implements the gyrogroup structure of three-velocities
 following Ungar (2006) <doi:10.1088/0143-0807/27/3/L02>. For general
 relativity, see the 'schwarzschild' package.
